												<div class="vers-no">25</div>
						<div class="vers-content">Once more Jesus laid his hands upon his eyes, and he began to see right; and soon he recovered, so that he could see everything clearly.</div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers173636" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">26</div>
						<div class="vers-content">Then he sent him back to his house; Go home, he said, and if thou shouldst enter the village, do not tell anyone of it.<span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
