						<div class="vers-content">And he called his disciples to him, and the multitude with them, and said to them, If any man has a mind to come my way, let him renounce self, and take up his cross, and follow me.</div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers173645" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">35</div>
						<div class="vers-content">The man who tries to save his life will lose it; it is the man who loses his life for my sake and for the gospelâ€™s sake, that will save it.</div>
